Subject: [PATCH v3 06/22] KVM: arm64: Simplify the CPUHP logic
Date:   Thu,  1 Sep 2022 19:17:41 -0700
Message-Id: <72481a7bc0ff08093f4f0f04cece877ee82de0cf.1662084396.git.isaku.yamahata@intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
